1. **Task 1**: The preseed fallback (task picker) now detects when the assessment phase failed entirely — producing a placeholder `assessment_missing.md` artifact instead of real analysis — and adjusts its behavior accordingly. Previously, the task picker would just treat whatever text was in the assessment file as the assessment, even if it was a placeholder saying "I couldn't assess the codebase." Now it knows when the assessment is a stub.

